name: Jeff Fortenberry
speech: Mr. FORTENBERRY. Mr. Speaker, on Monday, December 28, 2020, after  consulting with the Capitol physician regarding Covid restrictions, I  missed roll call vote No. 252 and No. 253. Had I been present, I would  have voted ``nay'' on No. 252 and ``aye'' on No. 253.
